ComicInfo.Title: A Domestic Drama In A Suburban Hell; Dead Girl Superstar
ComicInfo.Summary: In Los Angeles in the year 2064, the world has changed. The dead have risen and corpses live again. In a blackly comedic saga that only Guy Davis could illustrate, a zombie apocalypse like you have never seen engulfs the City of Angels.
